import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Card, CardContent, Grid, Button } from '@mui/material';
import SearchIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Search';
import ChatIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Chat';
import LocalHospitalIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LocalHospital';
import CalendarMonthIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CalendarMonth';
import PersonIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Person';
import { useHistory } from 'react-router-dom';

export default function MainApp() {
  const history = useHistory();
  const [userType, setUserType] = useState(null);
  const [userName, setUserName] = useState('');

  useEffect(() => {
    const userStr = localStorage.getItem('user');
    if (userStr) {
      const user = JSON.parse(userStr);
      setUserType(user.tipo);
      setUserName(user.nome);
    }
  }, []);

  return (
    <Box sx={{ minHeight: '100vh', background: 'radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, #23272f 60%, #181a20 100%)', p: { xs: 2, md: 6 } }}>
      <Box sx={{ maxWidth: 1100, mx: 'auto', mt: 6 }}>
        <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={800} color="#fff" align="center" mb={2}>
          Bem-vindo, {userName}!
        </Typography>
        <Typography color="#b0b8c1" align="center" mb={6} sx={{ fontSize: 20 }}>
          {userType === 'clinica' 
            ? 'Gerencie sua clínica, atendimentos e converse com pacientes.'
            : 'Encontre clínicas, agende consultas e converse com especialistas de forma simples e rápida.'}
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
          {userType === 'clinica' ? (
            // Cards para Clínicas
            <>
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 4, boxShadow: 8, background: 'rgba(30,34,44,0.96)', backdropFilter: 'blur(8px)', textAlign: 'center', transition: 'transform 0.2s', '&:hover': { transform: 'scale(1.04)', boxShadow: 12 } }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <LocalHospitalIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} color="#fff" mb={1}>Minha Clínica</Typography>
                    <Typography color="#b0b8c1" mb={2}>
                      Gerencie informações, horários e serviços da sua clínica.
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ borderRadius: 3, fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 17, background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2 60%, #0d47a1 100%)' }}>
                      Gerenciar
                    </Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 4, boxShadow: 8, background: 'rgba(30,34,44,0.96)', backdropFilter: 'blur(8px)', textAlign: 'center', transition: 'transform 0.2s', '&:hover': { transform: 'scale(1.04)', boxShadow: 12 } }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <CalendarMonthIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} color="#fff" mb={1}>Agendamentos</Typography>
                    <Typography color="#b0b8c1" mb={2}>
                      Visualize e gerencie todos os agendamentos da clínica.
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ borderRadius: 3, fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 17, background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2 60%, #0d47a1 100%)' }}>
                      Ver Agenda
                    </Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 4, boxShadow: 8, background: 'rgba(30,34,44,0.96)', backdropFilter: 'blur(8px)', textAlign: 'center', transition: 'transform 0.2s', '&:hover': { transform: 'scale(1.04)', boxShadow: 12 } }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <ChatIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} color="#fff" mb={1}>Chat</Typography>
                    <Typography color="#b0b8c1" mb={2}>
                      Converse com seus pacientes e gerencie atendimentos.
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ borderRadius: 3, fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 17, background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2 60%, #0d47a1 100%)' }}>
                      Acessar Chat
                    </Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            </>
          ) : (
            // Cards para Pacientes
            <>
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 4, boxShadow: 8, background: 'rgba(30,34,44,0.96)', backdropFilter: 'blur(8px)', textAlign: 'center', transition: 'transform 0.2s', '&:hover': { transform: 'scale(1.04)', boxShadow: 12 } }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <SearchIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} color="#fff" mb={1}>Buscar Clínicas</Typography>
                    <Typography color="#b0b8c1" mb={2}>
                      Encontre clínicas próximas por especialidade e localização.
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ borderRadius: 3, fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 17, background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2 60%, #0d47a1 100%)' }}>
                      Buscar
                    </Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 4, boxShadow: 8, background: 'rgba(30,34,44,0.96)', backdropFilter: 'blur(8px)', textAlign: 'center', transition: 'transform 0.2s', '&:hover': { transform: 'scale(1.04)', boxShadow: 12 } }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <CalendarMonthIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} color="#fff" mb={1}>Meus Agendamentos</Typography>
                    <Typography color="#b0b8c1" mb={2}>
                      Visualize e gerencie suas consultas agendadas.
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ borderRadius: 3, fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 17, background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2 60%, #0d47a1 100%)' }}>
                      Ver Agenda
                    </Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 4, boxShadow: 8, background: 'rgba(30,34,44,0.96)', backdropFilter: 'blur(8px)', textAlign: 'center', transition: 'transform 0.2s', '&:hover': { transform: 'scale(1.04)', boxShadow: 12 } }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <PersonIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#1976d2', mb: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} color="#fff" mb={1}>Meu Perfil</Typography>
                    <Typography color="#b0b8c1" mb={2}>
                      Gerencie seus dados pessoais e preferências.
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ borderRadius: 3, fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 17, background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2 60%, #0d47a1 100%)' }}>
                      Editar Perfil
                    </Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            </>
          )}
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
